Tokenized Carbon Credit L1
Overview

Tokenized Carbon Credit L1 enables transparent issuance, tracking, and trading of carbon credits using blockchain technology.

Features

Verifiable carbon credit tokens

Transparent emissions tracking

Automated carbon offset markets

Compliance reporting tools

Cross-market interoperability

Architecture
Carbon Asset Registry

Stores verified environmental assets.

Tokenization Engine

Converts credits into tradable tokens.

Market Settlement Layer

Handles trading and settlement.

Compliance Module

Tracks regulatory reporting.

Use Cases

Corporate carbon offsetting

Environmental trading markets

Sustainability reporting

Climate impact transparency
